        <mxCell id="TUgGetPv8wfsZy4MX2EW-119" parent="1" style="text;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;ij2dmu&quot; data-start=&quot;0&quot; data-end=&quot;26&quot;&gt;Functional Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;ynplfb&quot; data-start=&quot;28&quot; data-end=&quot;36&quot;&gt;User&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;37&quot; data-end=&quot;167&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1kdj5sr&quot; data-start=&quot;37&quot; data-end=&quot;83&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;40&quot; data-end=&quot;83&quot;&gt;User should be able to register and log in.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;faxrsg&quot; data-start=&quot;84&quot; data-end=&quot;122&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;87&quot; data-end=&quot;122&quot;&gt;User should be able to like videos.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;dcpuso&quot; data-start=&quot;123&quot; data-end=&quot;167&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;126&quot; data-end=&quot;167&quot;&gt;User should be able to comment on videos.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;75rql3&quot; data-start=&quot;169&quot; data-end=&quot;178&quot;&gt;Video&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;179&quot; data-end=&quot;657&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1vl7x4d&quot; data-start=&quot;179&quot; data-end=&quot;228&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;182&quot; data-end=&quot;228&quot;&gt;User should be able to search videos by title.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ujkijz&quot; data-start=&quot;229&quot; data-end=&quot;317&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;232&quot; data-end=&quot;317&quot;&gt;User should be able to view video catalog information such as metadata and thumbnail.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;tp9zj3&quot; data-start=&quot;318&quot; data-end=&quot;381&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;321&quot; data-end=&quot;381&quot;&gt;User should be able to play or stream videos using HLS/DASH.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;16mf2im&quot; data-start=&quot;382&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;385&quot; data-end=&quot;429&quot;&gt;User should be able to adjust video quality.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1788w3f&quot; data-start=&quot;430&quot; data-end=&quot;481&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;433&quot; data-end=&quot;481&quot;&gt;Content creator should be able to upload videos.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;ecxfc1&quot; data-start=&quot;482&quot; data-end=&quot;573&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;485&quot; data-end=&quot;573&quot;&gt;Uploaded videos should be processed into chunks and a manifest file should be generated.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;198q9mw&quot; data-start=&quot;574&quot; data-end=&quot;657&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;577&quot; data-end=&quot;657&quot;&gt;Video chunks should be served according to user bandwidth and device capability.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xa;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;659&quot; data-end=&quot;662&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;vvg2n8&quot; data-start=&quot;664&quot; data-end=&quot;694&quot;&gt;Non-Functional Requirements&lt;/h2&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;696&quot; data-end=&quot;1061&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;11813yq&quot; data-start=&quot;696&quot; data-end=&quot;747&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;699&quot; data-end=&quot;747&quot;&gt;The system should scale for &lt;strong data-start=&quot;727&quot; data-end=&quot;746&quot;&gt;1 billion users&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1y15qah&quot; data-start=&quot;748&quot; data-end=&quot;798&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;751&quot; data-end=&quot;798&quot;&gt;The system should be &lt;strong data-start=&quot;772&quot; data-end=&quot;797&quot;&gt;highly available 24/7&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;g8vylx&quot; data-start=&quot;799&quot; data-end=&quot;904&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;802&quot; data-end=&quot;904&quot;&gt;&lt;strong data-start=&quot;802&quot; data-end=&quot;855&quot;&gt;Availability should be preferred over consistency&lt;/strong&gt;, so the system can use &lt;strong data-start=&quot;879&quot; data-end=&quot;903&quot;&gt;eventual consistency&lt;/strong&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;pzlkm2&quot; data-start=&quot;905&quot; data-end=&quot;986&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;908&quot; data-end=&quot;986&quot;&gt;Video playback latency should be low, around &lt;strong data-start=&quot;953&quot; data-end=&quot;964&quot;&gt;1000 ms&lt;/strong&gt;, to reduce buffering.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;vm7xfb&quot; data-start=&quot;987&quot; data-end=&quot;1061&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;990&quot; data-end=&quot;1061&quot;&gt;The system should support smooth and reliable streaming at large scale.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xa;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1063&quot; data-end=&quot;1066&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;h2 data-section-id=&quot;1xozff1&quot; data-start=&quot;1068&quot; data-end=&quot;1084&quot;&gt;API Endpoints&lt;/h2&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;14uiayb&quot; data-start=&quot;1086&quot; data-end=&quot;1102&quot;&gt;Auth Service&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;1103&quot; data-end=&quot;1229&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;b6rirw&quot; data-start=&quot;1103&quot; data-end=&quot;1157&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1106&quot; data-end=&quot;1157&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1106&quot; data-end=&quot;1131&quot;&gt;POST /api/user/register&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1131&quot; data-end=&quot;1134&quot;&gt;&#xa;Register a new user.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1wbjq1b&quot; data-start=&quot;1159&quot; data-end=&quot;1229&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1162&quot; data-end=&quot;1229&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1162&quot; data-end=&quot;1184&quot;&gt;POST /api/user/login&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1184&quot; data-end=&quot;1187&quot;&gt;&#xa;Authenticate user and return JWT token.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xa;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1231&quot; data-end=&quot;1234&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1528yfx&quot; data-start=&quot;1236&quot; data-end=&quot;1265&quot;&gt;Video Search and Playback&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;1266&quot; data-end=&quot;1566&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1sqx6hv&quot; data-start=&quot;1266&quot; data-end=&quot;1368&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1269&quot; data-end=&quot;1368&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1269&quot; data-end=&quot;1310&quot;&gt;GET /api/video/search?name={video_name}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1310&quot; data-end=&quot;1313&quot;&gt;&#xa;Search videos by title and return paginated results.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;puyqzm&quot; data-start=&quot;1370&quot; data-end=&quot;1425&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1373&quot; data-end=&quot;1425&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1373&quot; data-end=&quot;1400&quot;&gt;GET /api/video/{video_id}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1400&quot; data-end=&quot;1403&quot;&gt;&#xa;Get video metadata.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;skx8i9&quot; data-start=&quot;1427&quot; data-end=&quot;1512&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1430&quot; data-end=&quot;1512&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1430&quot; data-end=&quot;1462&quot;&gt;GET /api/video/play/{video_id}&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1462&quot; data-end=&quot;1465&quot;&gt;&#xa;Get manifest file / stream URL for playback.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;etkm2x&quot; data-start=&quot;1514&quot; data-end=&quot;1566&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1517&quot; data-end=&quot;1566&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1517&quot; data-end=&quot;1541&quot;&gt;POST /api/video/upload&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1541&quot; data-end=&quot;1544&quot;&gt;&#xa;Upload a new video.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;/ol&gt;&#xa;&lt;hr data-start=&quot;1568&quot; data-end=&quot;1571&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;h3 data-section-id=&quot;1h1bv6a&quot; data-start=&quot;1573&quot; data-end=&quot;1597&quot;&gt;Interaction Services&lt;/h3&gt;&#xa;&lt;ol data-start=&quot;1598&quot; data-end=&quot;1852&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;1ynof3u&quot; data-start=&quot;1598&quot; data-end=&quot;1653&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1601&quot; data-end=&quot;1653&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1601&quot; data-end=&quot;1634&quot;&gt;POST /api/video/{video_id}/like&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1634&quot; data-end=&quot;1637&quot;&gt;&#xa;Like a video.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;geerkz&quot; data-start=&quot;1655&quot; data-end=&quot;1714&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1658&quot; data-end=&quot;1714&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1658&quot; data-end=&quot;1693&quot;&gt;DELETE /api/video/{video_id}/like&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1693&quot; data-end=&quot;1696&quot;&gt;&#xa;Unlike a video.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;atbs5j&quot; data-start=&quot;1716&quot; data-end=&quot;1780&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1719&quot; data-end=&quot;1780&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1719&quot; data-end=&quot;1756&quot;&gt;POST /api/video/{video_id}/comments&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1756&quot; data-end=&quot;1759&quot;&gt;&#xa;Add a new comment.&lt;/p&gt;&#xa;&lt;/li&gt;&#xa;&lt;li data-section-id=&quot;15qqig&quot; data-start=&quot;1782&quot; data-end=&quot;1852&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&#xa;&lt;p data-start=&quot;1785&quot; data-end=&quot;1852&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;code data-start=&quot;1785&quot; data-end=&quot;1821&quot;&gt;GET /api/video/{video_id}/comments&lt;/code&gt;&lt;br data-start=&quot;1821&quot; data-end=&quot;1824&quot;&gt;&#xa;Fetch paginated comments.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;" vertex="1">
          <mxGeometry height="3250" width="1590" x="-214.61" y="10860" as="geometry" />
        </mxCell>
